WEBVTT

01:32.270 --> 01:34.990
[How dare you!?]

01:35.020 --> 01:38.000
[Episode 8]

01:38.150 --> 01:39.280
When that day comes,

01:40.150 --> 01:43.120
I hope you all remember
what was said on this boat today—

01:43.120 --> 01:44.320
your heartfelt words

01:45.200 --> 01:46.400
and lofty ambitions.

01:48.310 --> 01:49.350
Stand tall

01:50.590 --> 01:52.390
and be the backbone of Great Xia.

01:54.200 --> 01:55.509
It was clearly just rhetoric

01:55.509 --> 01:56.840
to recruit scholars.

01:57.509 --> 01:59.039
But why, after hearing it,

01:59.950 --> 02:01.230
do I feel like crying?

02:02.280 --> 02:03.210
Your Majesty...

02:04.430 --> 02:06.040
places such high hopes on us.

02:07.070 --> 02:07.330
I...

02:08.430 --> 02:09.090
I really...

02:09.280 --> 02:10.590
How inappropriate!

02:11.400 --> 02:12.590
How can an emperor

02:12.960 --> 02:14.020
speak so casually?

02:15.240 --> 02:16.960
Just because of the hardships,

02:16.960 --> 02:19.430
you want to turn poor scholars' bodies

02:19.520 --> 02:20.490
into pawns

02:20.630 --> 02:22.430
and sacrifice their lives for you,

02:22.430 --> 02:24.150
depose the Empress Dowager,
and get rid of Prince Duan.

02:24.150 --> 02:25.560
Because you are surviving precariously,

02:25.560 --> 02:27.420
you cannot express your own will.

02:27.560 --> 02:28.800
You have obstacles everywhere you head,

02:28.800 --> 02:30.840
so you cannot rectify court discipline.

02:30.840 --> 02:32.100
As the mighty Emperor,

02:32.560 --> 02:34.150
if you don't even have such courage,

02:34.150 --> 02:36.240
how can you talk about
paying fortunes for talent,

02:36.240 --> 02:38.170
pushing others to be the backbone?

02:39.400 --> 02:41.079
The common people in my village—

02:41.079 --> 02:42.120
every household—

02:43.400 --> 02:45.590
all toil in the fields all day,

02:45.840 --> 02:47.360
saving every grain they can,

02:47.360 --> 02:49.020
yet have barely enough to eat.

02:49.360 --> 02:51.090
My younger brother and sister,

02:52.150 --> 02:53.810
starved to death during a year

02:54.280 --> 02:57.280
of poor harvest
shortly after they were born.

02:57.680 --> 02:59.030
Such heavy taxes—

02:59.560 --> 03:01.960
did they truly go where they should?

03:06.840 --> 03:09.680
The Central Army has been fighting
against Yan State for years.

03:09.680 --> 03:11.240
Yet the soldier provisions

03:11.240 --> 03:13.170
are mixed with 30% sand and stones.

03:13.960 --> 03:15.280
As soon as I arrived in the capital,

03:15.280 --> 03:19.010
I saw the Court of Revision beat to death
a woman crying for justice.

03:19.310 --> 03:20.240
Your Majesty...

03:21.680 --> 03:22.480
Your Majesty!

03:22.750 --> 03:24.360
Have you truly opened your eyes

03:24.360 --> 03:26.420
to see what I've described?

03:36.240 --> 03:36.710
Li,

03:37.430 --> 03:38.150
no need to say all this.

03:38.150 --> 03:39.480
Who was it that just said

03:39.520 --> 03:40.400
if they could meet the Emperor,

03:40.400 --> 03:42.310
they would kowtow and offer advice
even at the cost of their lives?

03:42.310 --> 03:44.310
Now the Emperor is right before you.

03:44.630 --> 03:46.290
What's happened to all of you?

03:46.360 --> 03:47.079
Gone mute?

03:49.240 --> 03:51.750
His Majesty
did punish the Minister of Revenue.

03:51.750 --> 03:53.010
It caused quite a stir.

03:53.360 --> 03:55.490
I believe everyone has heard about it.

03:55.590 --> 03:57.190
As for the case of the runaway horse,

03:57.190 --> 03:58.190
His Majesty also found a way

03:58.190 --> 04:00.190
to bring
Grand Tutor Wei's family to justice.

04:00.190 --> 04:00.590
But

04:01.150 --> 04:02.680
rumors among the people say

04:02.840 --> 04:04.080
it was Prince Duan's doing.

04:04.080 --> 04:05.810
Every household in my hometown

04:06.000 --> 04:07.590
were burning incense
praying for his blessing.

04:07.590 --> 04:08.810
No matter who did it,

04:10.360 --> 04:11.690
have the people's lives

04:13.590 --> 04:14.560
improved?

04:21.630 --> 04:23.490
The incense from every household

04:24.510 --> 04:26.430
was burned in vain at the end of the day.

04:26.430 --> 04:26.800
Li.

04:26.920 --> 04:27.270
Li.

04:27.920 --> 04:29.050
Defying the Emperor

04:29.070 --> 04:30.120
is a capital offense.

04:30.120 --> 04:32.980
I don't mind
spilling my blood on this pleasure boat

04:33.120 --> 04:35.120
to prove my determination with death.

04:35.120 --> 04:37.070
This perfectly fulfills my wish.

04:37.310 --> 04:38.170
-Mr. Li.
-Wait!

04:40.000 --> 04:40.330
Mr...

04:41.800 --> 04:42.360
Mr. Li.

04:43.190 --> 04:44.720
His Majesty came here today

04:44.750 --> 04:47.080
not to drag everyone into court factions.

04:47.870 --> 04:48.400
Besides,

04:49.190 --> 04:51.070
those who hold positions without merit,

04:51.070 --> 04:52.800
also those of the royal family,

04:52.920 --> 04:54.380
their deaths mean little.

04:54.870 --> 04:57.159
But what crime
have the common people committed?

04:57.159 --> 04:58.890
The situation has become dire.

04:59.360 --> 05:00.360
Unfair taxation,

05:00.720 --> 05:01.850
corrupt officials,

05:02.270 --> 05:04.730
rampant corruption, and empty treasury...

05:05.070 --> 05:06.600
Our abilities are limited.

05:07.040 --> 05:08.510
Though we have solutions,

05:09.170 --> 05:10.390
one hand can't clap.

05:11.270 --> 05:12.950
That's why we need your help.

05:14.270 --> 05:15.250
I'm not eloquent

05:15.870 --> 05:18.000
and cannot speak of grand principles.

05:18.310 --> 05:20.070
But besides being a consort,

05:21.830 --> 05:23.560
I am also a citizen of Great Xia.

05:25.160 --> 05:26.430
I love this land.

05:27.430 --> 05:29.070
I also want to do something

05:29.070 --> 05:30.600
for the people living here.

05:31.190 --> 05:32.200
But I am stupid.

05:33.600 --> 05:35.060
I can only implore you all.

05:36.000 --> 05:38.530
This is not for any tyrant
or demonic consort,

05:39.390 --> 05:39.990
but for...

05:44.360 --> 05:45.890
our elders of our homeland,

05:48.070 --> 05:50.470
and for our deceased brothers and sisters.

05:52.630 --> 05:54.360
Please consider it carefully.

06:17.270 --> 06:18.400
If you wish to leave,

06:19.540 --> 06:20.600
I will not stop you.

06:21.680 --> 06:23.540
If you wish to serve as officials,

06:23.630 --> 06:25.030
I will fully support you,

06:25.830 --> 06:27.430
even if not under my command.

06:31.630 --> 06:32.760
I don't understand.

06:33.830 --> 06:35.090
Why are you doing this?

06:35.600 --> 06:37.330
There is no particular reason.

06:38.390 --> 06:39.920
It's only because I believe

06:40.920 --> 06:42.230
that wherever you are,

06:43.510 --> 06:44.440
whatever you do,

06:45.240 --> 06:47.440
you surely act for the good of Great Xia.

06:48.390 --> 06:48.990
Even if...

06:50.560 --> 06:51.760
it means opposing me.

06:54.750 --> 06:55.920
I...

06:56.750 --> 06:57.870
I...

06:59.000 --> 07:00.070
I never understood before why,

07:00.070 --> 07:03.130
when speaking to the royals,
we condescend ourselves.

07:03.830 --> 07:06.560
Are we born to be trampled upon?

07:09.270 --> 07:10.430
Now I understand.

07:11.120 --> 07:11.750
We are just

07:13.390 --> 07:15.990
ever-growing and resilient—
the foundation.

07:19.190 --> 07:22.270
I was born with a terrible illness

07:24.430 --> 07:26.890
and have only
two or three years left to live.

07:27.630 --> 07:28.890
May I ask Your Majesty,

07:29.430 --> 07:32.870
will I live to see peace and prosperity,

07:34.560 --> 07:36.040
harmony and abundance?

07:39.850 --> 07:41.710
This is my promise as the Emperor.

07:56.430 --> 07:57.450
I, Cen Jintian,

07:57.950 --> 07:59.680
am willing to serve Your Majesty

07:59.680 --> 08:00.810
with all my loyalty.

08:18.800 --> 08:20.800
Even if they are just 2D characters,

08:21.160 --> 08:22.360
the suffering they endure

08:22.360 --> 08:23.920
is real pain to them.

08:25.600 --> 08:27.530
I've always overlooked this fact,

08:28.070 --> 08:30.000
thinking I was different from them.

08:30.000 --> 08:31.270
But how can I be certain

08:31.290 --> 08:33.220
that I'm not a 2D character myself?

08:35.320 --> 08:36.320
Since we're here,

08:37.240 --> 08:38.700
we might as well accept it.

08:51.910 --> 08:52.960
Hey, quick!

08:53.080 --> 08:53.720
There's a leak!

08:53.720 --> 08:54.250
Boatman!

08:54.360 --> 08:55.560
Your boat is leaking!

08:58.910 --> 09:00.280
Plug it!

09:09.350 --> 09:11.480
-Mr. Yang, our boat is leaking!
-Help!

09:19.550 --> 09:20.500
S-Same here!

09:23.320 --> 09:23.960
Save them quickly!

09:23.960 --> 09:25.120
Make sure to rescue all the scholars!

09:25.120 --> 09:25.780
-Yes!
-Yes!

09:59.240 --> 09:59.660
Quick!

10:18.840 --> 10:19.590
Grab it!

10:43.120 --> 10:43.670
Xu Yao!

10:44.360 --> 10:45.240
Get up!

10:47.670 --> 10:50.000
This isn't how your story ends
in the book.

10:50.510 --> 10:52.240
You still have a vendetta to settle.

10:52.240 --> 10:53.500
You're still so young.

10:53.670 --> 10:55.870
You must have many things you want to do.

10:56.200 --> 10:57.440
In your story, your ending

10:57.440 --> 10:59.670
is to be second only to one,
above thousands,

10:59.670 --> 11:00.960
wealthy and healthy.

11:00.170 --> 11:03.160
♪ Standing in the hurricane,
watching the fire rise ♪

11:01.630 --> 11:03.720
I give my life to the wise master,

11:03.480 --> 11:06.180
♪ Dancing on the blade's edge, I thread
through blood, writing my wild ode ♪

11:04.440 --> 11:07.030
and I die for the country.

11:06.520 --> 11:07.400
♪ I am not one of the gentle ones ♪

11:07.430 --> 11:10.970
♪ How could my thoughts
be tethered to the soft begonia?  ♪

11:08.390 --> 11:09.670
I love this land.

11:10.750 --> 11:12.390
I also want to do something

11:12.260 --> 11:13.710
♪ Do not speak to me
of what's inappropriate ♪

11:12.390 --> 11:13.730
for the people living here.

11:13.730 --> 11:15.210
♪ I am the moral order ♪

11:14.200 --> 11:15.320
If that's truly the case,

11:15.320 --> 11:16.320
then it would fulfill

11:15.360 --> 11:18.340
♪ The gleam of the blade
tempers feathers into a phantom Phoenix  ♪

11:17.000 --> 11:18.470
my childhood aspirations.

11:18.470 --> 11:19.390
♪ And these Phoenix bones of mine ♪

11:19.460 --> 11:24.350
♪ Empower me
to pierce through the wind and waves ♪

11:19.550 --> 11:20.810
May I ask Your Majesty,

11:21.440 --> 11:24.910
will I live to see peace and prosperity,

11:25.870 --> 11:27.600
harmony and abundance?

11:25.910 --> 11:27.600
♪ Allow me ♪

11:27.630 --> 11:30.180
♪ To not linger in shame,
to not give way ♪

11:30.210 --> 11:32.960
♪ To not be faithless,
to not admit defeat ♪

11:33.470 --> 11:36.360
♪ A body of stubborn pride
rises to shout that I ♪

11:35.960 --> 11:36.460
These people

11:36.460 --> 11:38.950
♪ Was never a creature
meant for the shallows ♪

11:36.870 --> 11:38.530
must all be Prince Duan's men!

11:39.420 --> 11:40.420
♪ Allow me ♪

11:40.490 --> 11:41.750
And they call me the demonic consort?

11:40.800 --> 11:42.130
♪ To never pause ♪

11:42.550 --> 11:43.550
♪ Allow me ♪

11:42.670 --> 11:43.730
I am nothing compared to him

11:43.730 --> 11:45.100
♪ To dare to shatter my bones ♪

11:44.030 --> 11:45.370
when it comes to being evil.

11:45.370 --> 11:51.180
♪ Wherever I stand,
I dare to write a legend of glory ♪

11:46.360 --> 11:46.910
But,

11:47.520 --> 11:48.980
even if he were truly a god,

11:49.360 --> 11:50.840
I would never surrender!

11:53.080 --> 11:54.000
Let's get him!

12:14.000 --> 12:15.380
♪ Allow me ♪

12:15.400 --> 12:17.850
♪ To not linger in shame,
to not give way ♪

12:18.500 --> 12:20.920
♪ To not be faithless,
to not admit defeat ♪

12:20.240 --> 12:20.700
Come on.

12:21.080 --> 12:21.720
Give me your hand

12:21.430 --> 12:24.330
♪ A body of stubborn pride
rises to shout that I ♪

12:24.360 --> 12:26.940
♪ Was never a creature
meant for the shallows ♪

12:25.030 --> 12:26.030
What are you hesitating for?

12:26.030 --> 12:26.630
Hurry up!

12:27.380 --> 12:28.510
♪ Allow me ♪

12:28.760 --> 12:30.180
♪ To never pause ♪

12:30.420 --> 12:31.470
♪ Allow me ♪

12:31.800 --> 12:33.190
♪ To dare to shatter my bones ♪

12:33.440 --> 12:41.280
♪ Wherever I stand,
I dare to write a legend of glory ♪

12:34.770 --> 12:35.250
Cen.

12:37.200 --> 12:38.260
It's all right now.

12:50.270 --> 12:51.930
Don't leave any of them alive.

12:53.510 --> 12:54.150
Wanyin.

12:55.670 --> 12:57.000
Interesting.

13:08.720 --> 13:09.580
Your Highness!

13:09.750 --> 13:10.930
There's a skilled fighter.

13:10.930 --> 13:13.060
Their martial skills far exceed ours.

13:13.240 --> 13:14.550
The guards will hold them back.

13:14.550 --> 13:16.080
Please leave immediately.

14:35.720 --> 14:36.360
Du...

14:58.600 --> 14:59.400
It's okay now.

14:59.820 --> 15:00.750
Cover yourself.

15:02.440 --> 15:03.080
Thank you.

15:41.790 --> 15:42.790
Compared to them,

15:44.350 --> 15:45.410
my pain is nothing.

15:50.270 --> 15:51.200
Do you remember?

15:52.270 --> 15:53.670
That day at Banyue House,

15:55.080 --> 15:55.870
Du Shan said

15:59.360 --> 16:01.890
it was his final attempt
at the imperial exam.

16:03.670 --> 16:04.720
His poem

16:06.720 --> 16:09.440
had just begun
to spread throughout the capital.

16:09.440 --> 16:11.040
It had just given him hope...

16:12.510 --> 16:14.240
only for him to end up like this.

16:23.150 --> 16:24.610
Try to see it differently.

16:25.320 --> 16:26.650
Sacrificing one person

16:27.270 --> 16:28.800
to ensure others' survival

16:29.750 --> 16:31.280
is sometimes unavoidable.

16:36.630 --> 16:37.750
Xiahou Po...

16:38.840 --> 16:40.370
No matter if he foresaw this

16:40.870 --> 16:41.960
or tracked us here,

16:44.000 --> 16:46.060
how dare he kill as soon as he got here—

16:46.270 --> 16:47.970
right in front of me too.

16:50.270 --> 16:51.600
He simply wants to intimidate

16:51.600 --> 16:54.060
me, an emperor
who suddenly wants to resist.

16:54.750 --> 16:55.610
I was wondering

16:57.720 --> 17:00.240
what tragic past he had in his backstory

17:01.000 --> 17:03.440
that made him feel compelled
by government corruption

17:03.440 --> 17:04.720
to seize the throne.

17:05.510 --> 17:07.640
But the people he just tried to kill...

17:09.720 --> 17:11.250
are the future officials,

17:11.960 --> 17:13.490
the backbone of our nation,

17:14.349 --> 17:16.680
and the final hope
to stabilize Great Xia.

17:16.829 --> 17:18.089
If he is a 2D character,

17:19.349 --> 17:21.349
then he's killing innocent people.

17:21.720 --> 17:23.450
If he comes from a higher level,

17:24.400 --> 17:26.060
knowing exactly who they are,

17:26.109 --> 17:27.910
yet still choosing to kill them,

17:28.720 --> 17:30.980
then it's for his own future as a warlord,

17:31.640 --> 17:32.920
condemning countless people to death

17:32.920 --> 17:34.350
during this drought.

17:38.400 --> 17:38.750
I,

17:40.270 --> 17:41.070
Yu Wanyin,

17:42.880 --> 17:44.140
will never allow that.

17:45.050 --> 17:47.110
Since they call me a demonic consort,

17:49.350 --> 17:51.950
I'll show them
what being demonic truly means.

17:54.610 --> 17:58.210
[Prince Duan's Mansion]

18:02.640 --> 18:03.100
Get out.

18:14.270 --> 18:15.130
Your Highness.

18:19.550 --> 18:20.030
What?

18:27.350 --> 18:29.310
That was more than 20 men.

18:32.350 --> 18:34.550
All killed by one person?

18:35.230 --> 18:36.760
If I hadn't left first,

18:38.400 --> 18:40.360
would I have died there too?

18:42.250 --> 18:43.510
It is my incompetency.

18:44.160 --> 18:46.160
I've failed Your Highness's trust.

18:50.790 --> 18:52.070
Did you see the faces

18:54.310 --> 18:55.440
of those on the boat?

18:55.960 --> 18:57.760
Everyone who saw their faces...

18:59.920 --> 19:01.280
But please rest assured, Your Highness.

19:01.280 --> 19:02.810
I will make up for my failure

19:02.960 --> 19:05.090
and identify them as soon as possible.

19:09.830 --> 19:10.470
Lord Fan.

19:11.830 --> 19:13.030
What did you discover

19:15.280 --> 19:16.310
at West Mountain?

19:18.590 --> 19:19.350
I...

19:19.880 --> 19:21.570
I led our men

19:22.830 --> 19:24.290
and stopped the carriage,

19:24.440 --> 19:25.790
only to discover that His Majesty

19:25.790 --> 19:27.350
had already moved the imperial guards

19:27.350 --> 19:28.830
and set up an ambush there.

19:34.880 --> 19:35.510
Well...

19:37.440 --> 19:38.110
Very well.

19:41.160 --> 19:42.270
Who was

19:44.750 --> 19:45.680
in the carriage?

19:47.240 --> 19:47.880
It was...

19:48.440 --> 19:48.970
It was...

19:49.880 --> 19:50.350
It...

19:51.240 --> 19:51.920
Who was it?

19:52.640 --> 19:53.510
I-I-It was

19:53.750 --> 19:54.770
Eunuch An!

19:57.790 --> 19:58.320
Useless!

20:13.240 --> 20:14.680
Who told me

20:16.790 --> 20:19.320
this was a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity,

20:20.560 --> 20:23.280
that we could act
without anyone else knowing?

20:24.880 --> 20:26.400
Who told me

20:30.670 --> 20:32.270
that we were well-prepared?

20:35.640 --> 20:37.790
And that while it may not be foolproof,

20:40.160 --> 20:42.510
we have a high chance of succeeding?

20:46.830 --> 20:48.200
Was it you?

20:56.220 --> 20:57.280
No, Your Highness!

20:57.790 --> 20:58.250
Your...

21:00.830 --> 21:01.830
Your Highness...

21:02.400 --> 21:02.860
Your...

21:04.720 --> 21:07.350
You are truly my excellent strategist.

21:08.200 --> 21:11.200
You, one person alone,
killed over a hundred of my men.

21:13.750 --> 21:15.640
Go join them now.

21:27.720 --> 21:29.180
Xiahou Dan.

21:42.640 --> 21:45.070
I underestimated you.

21:50.170 --> 21:53.030
[Yongyan Hall]

21:55.030 --> 21:57.430
Still thinking about what happened today?

21:59.790 --> 22:01.030
After calming down,

22:02.110 --> 22:03.570
I'm even more certain now.

22:03.590 --> 22:04.520
Certain of what?

22:04.680 --> 22:06.610
Prince Duan must be a 2D character.

22:07.240 --> 22:08.300
Why do you say that?

22:10.110 --> 22:12.440
West Mountain and East Lake are far apart.

22:12.680 --> 22:14.440
Prince Duan has limited forces.

22:14.440 --> 22:16.100
If he had a god's perspective,

22:16.400 --> 22:18.000
knowing we were at East Lake,

22:18.310 --> 22:20.960
why did they send
most of their forces to West Mountain

22:20.960 --> 22:22.290
to surround our decoys?

22:24.680 --> 22:26.940
He wasn't completely confident either.

22:27.350 --> 22:28.150
That's right.

22:30.350 --> 22:32.680
And the people
who ambushed us at East Lake

22:33.240 --> 22:34.300
were few in number.

22:35.920 --> 22:37.650
They were clearly unprepared.

22:37.750 --> 22:38.410
Otherwise,

22:38.880 --> 22:41.880
it wouldn't have ended with
just one scholar's death.

22:43.350 --> 22:43.880
Exactly.

22:45.400 --> 22:46.640
And at East Lake,

22:47.350 --> 22:49.030
they clearly didn't anticipate

22:49.030 --> 22:50.630
Mr. Bei's fighting ability.

22:52.070 --> 22:53.000
Just as you said,

22:54.790 --> 22:56.650
they killed someone in front of us

22:56.680 --> 22:57.790
to intimidate us.

22:59.240 --> 23:01.440
There's no reason they could have lost.

23:01.920 --> 23:03.960
I don't believe it if their loss

23:06.240 --> 23:07.700
was a calculated move too.

23:08.200 --> 23:08.750
So

23:10.000 --> 23:11.070
Prince Duan definitely isn't

23:11.070 --> 23:12.600
someone at a level above us.

23:14.310 --> 23:15.110
He's exposed.

23:17.030 --> 23:17.550
Oh no.

23:18.720 --> 23:19.520
What's wrong?

23:19.920 --> 23:21.830
He might not be
the only one who's been exposed.

23:21.830 --> 23:22.830
Who else is there?

23:23.160 --> 23:25.160
That shout of yours was impressive,

23:25.160 --> 23:27.160
but it might have exposed you to him.

23:29.310 --> 23:30.240
That's it?

23:30.510 --> 23:31.400
"That's it?"

23:35.350 --> 23:36.590
Your personal safety

23:37.590 --> 23:38.990
is of utmost importance.

23:45.270 --> 23:47.130
Actually, even without my shout,

23:47.680 --> 23:50.610
Prince Duan would have suspected me
sooner or later.

23:51.680 --> 23:53.280
But I still don't understand

23:53.960 --> 23:54.720
how our plan

23:54.880 --> 23:56.540
was leaked in the first place.

23:58.720 --> 24:01.780
Only Bei Zhou and the secret guards
knew our itinerary.

24:02.270 --> 24:02.790
But...

24:03.110 --> 24:06.440
in the original story,
they protected me until the very end.

24:06.880 --> 24:07.940
So it can't be them.

24:09.110 --> 24:10.970
The scholars, before meeting us,

24:11.030 --> 24:12.310
had no idea who we were.

24:13.110 --> 24:14.570
So it can't be them either.

24:16.880 --> 24:18.030
Then who can it be?

24:19.350 --> 24:21.950
Actually,
besides those people we mentioned,

24:22.000 --> 24:23.880
there's one more person
who might have leaked information.

24:23.880 --> 24:25.410
That's Xiahou Dan himself.

24:25.960 --> 24:26.960
Just as he said...

24:28.270 --> 24:29.600
Sacrificing one person

24:30.200 --> 24:31.730
to ensure others' survival

24:33.160 --> 24:34.690
is sometimes unavoidable.

24:35.160 --> 24:36.820
Sacrificing one 2D character

24:36.880 --> 24:39.010
-for greater benefits.
-Drag him out!

24:39.200 --> 24:40.000
After all,

24:40.000 --> 24:41.240
-he doesn't think their lives...
-Drag him out!

24:41.240 --> 24:43.070
-I'm telling the truth.
-Are that important.

24:43.070 --> 24:43.870
Your Majesty!

24:49.110 --> 24:50.640
They're all 2D characters—

24:52.640 --> 24:54.770
all promising talents in their prime.

24:56.000 --> 24:57.330
In the blink of an eye...

25:05.720 --> 25:07.050
Am I overthinking this?

25:07.960 --> 25:09.620
If he can't be trusted either,

25:10.030 --> 25:11.160
then in this palace,

25:11.640 --> 25:12.960
who can I trust?

25:13.000 --> 25:13.750
What are you thinking about?

25:13.750 --> 25:14.280
Nothing.

25:16.030 --> 25:17.030
I'll investigate

25:17.350 --> 25:18.080
this slowly.

25:19.440 --> 25:20.370
You're injured.

25:21.240 --> 25:22.700
You need to rest properly.

25:25.550 --> 25:26.550
You may leave now.

25:27.880 --> 25:30.080
You forgot? You've fallen out of favor.

25:31.070 --> 25:32.150
Xie Yong'er is coming soon.

25:32.150 --> 25:32.680
Go ahead.

25:35.830 --> 25:36.360
Yes, yes.

25:37.920 --> 25:39.250
Then I'll take my leave.

25:39.910 --> 25:40.240
Wait.

25:41.880 --> 25:43.410
How are you going to explain

25:43.750 --> 25:45.010
the wound on your hand?

25:51.830 --> 25:52.290
Get out!

25:52.880 --> 25:54.610
Your Majesty, please spare me!

25:59.680 --> 26:01.720
Which cross-eyed imperial physician

26:01.720 --> 26:02.750
bandaged this

26:03.240 --> 26:04.680
in such a ghastly manner?

26:09.240 --> 26:10.240
It's not that bad.

26:10.790 --> 26:12.320
How can His Majesty do this?

26:12.720 --> 26:15.830
He only cares for the newcomers
and ignores those that have been around.

26:15.830 --> 26:17.270
Even if Master made a mistake,

26:17.270 --> 26:19.600
he shouldn't take it out on Your Highness.

26:20.880 --> 26:22.400
I just got a small cut

26:22.400 --> 26:23.400
from a broken cup.

26:23.720 --> 26:25.780
How can this be blamed on His Majesty?

26:25.920 --> 26:27.550
But I clearly saw it.

26:27.920 --> 26:28.440
Madam,

26:29.270 --> 26:31.310
I suddenly want some sweet porridge.

26:31.310 --> 26:32.640
Could you make me a bowl?

26:39.440 --> 26:41.240
Madam Bei is His Majesty's person.

26:41.240 --> 26:42.240
Watch what you say

26:42.590 --> 26:43.720
and don't upset her.

26:43.720 --> 26:44.790
I'm not afraid.

26:46.350 --> 26:48.080
I'm just worried about My Lady.

26:48.720 --> 26:50.110
You could have been with your beloved,

26:50.110 --> 26:51.680
living a happy life.

26:52.830 --> 26:55.240
But now you're trapped in this palace,

26:56.440 --> 26:58.720
dealing with that tyrant every day.

26:59.680 --> 27:02.140
He even has people
watching you constantly.

27:03.000 --> 27:04.590
Serving the emperor is like
being with a tiger.

27:04.590 --> 27:05.520
Watch your head.

27:07.000 --> 27:08.160
How does Mei still remember

27:08.160 --> 27:10.550
my original character
of secretly loving Prince Duan?

27:10.550 --> 27:12.240
After being with me for so long,

27:12.240 --> 27:13.840
why hasn't she caught on yet?

27:22.400 --> 27:22.790
Du,

27:24.830 --> 27:25.440
you always

27:26.200 --> 27:27.030
found me

27:28.000 --> 27:28.550
stingy.

27:30.240 --> 27:33.500
Today I bought the finest
and most expensive Huadiao wine.

27:34.920 --> 27:35.920
Wherever you are,

27:36.590 --> 27:37.250
drink more.

27:45.310 --> 27:46.310
In Du's lifetime,

27:47.030 --> 27:48.620
his ambitions were unfulfilled,

27:48.620 --> 27:50.480
he had no way to serve his country,

27:50.750 --> 27:52.950
and poured all his passion into poetry.

27:53.240 --> 27:53.790
Now,

27:54.550 --> 27:55.880
having met a wise ruler,

27:56.510 --> 27:59.070
-we will take on Du's sincerity...
-What's wrong?

27:59.070 --> 28:01.130
and spare no effort to help Great Xia.

28:02.400 --> 28:02.830
Du,

28:04.510 --> 28:05.310
just watch us.

28:08.350 --> 28:09.550
After what happened,

28:10.270 --> 28:11.600
you must all understand

28:12.830 --> 28:14.960
that to work with me, a puppet emperor,

28:15.680 --> 28:17.540
to do something real for Great Xia

28:18.550 --> 28:20.210
requires taking great risks.

28:20.750 --> 28:22.080
If you wish to withdraw,

28:22.550 --> 28:23.810
it's understandable.

28:24.920 --> 28:25.510
However,

28:26.510 --> 28:28.680
you have already been involved
in confidential matters.

28:28.680 --> 28:29.340
Forgive me,

28:29.960 --> 28:31.020
but I cannot let you

28:31.240 --> 28:32.570
return home on your own.

28:33.270 --> 28:34.530
I hope you understand.

28:37.160 --> 28:38.890
What do you mean, Your Majesty?

28:41.240 --> 28:42.440
Do you want to kill us?

28:46.550 --> 28:47.000
No.

28:48.240 --> 28:49.440
I will find you a place

28:50.200 --> 28:51.750
far from this quagmire.

28:53.000 --> 28:54.110
I won't force you

28:55.110 --> 28:56.110
to offer counsel

28:56.720 --> 28:58.000
or act as advisors.

28:58.960 --> 29:00.620
You just need to study in peace

29:01.310 --> 29:03.970
until the situation
in the capital stabilizes.

29:04.720 --> 29:05.250
No matter

29:05.550 --> 29:06.810
who sits on the throne,

29:07.400 --> 29:07.830
you

29:09.310 --> 29:10.770
will still be yourselves—

29:11.200 --> 29:13.070
honest and capable talents.

29:13.590 --> 29:14.590
When that time comes,

29:14.590 --> 29:16.250
use your knowledge and skills

29:16.510 --> 29:18.170
to become virtuous ministers

29:19.590 --> 29:21.250
remembered for generations.

29:36.960 --> 29:37.350
I,

29:37.810 --> 29:38.860
Yang Duojie...

29:39.240 --> 29:39.640
I,

29:40.030 --> 29:40.720
Wang Zhao...

29:40.720 --> 29:41.070
I,

29:41.590 --> 29:42.250
Li Yunxi...

29:42.720 --> 29:43.070
I,

29:43.350 --> 29:43.960
Er Lan,

29:44.400 --> 29:47.030
am willing to serve
Your Majesty with utmost loyalty

29:47.030 --> 29:48.160
only for Great Xia's

29:48.270 --> 29:49.270
peace.

29:50.680 --> 29:52.160
I don't have much time left

29:52.960 --> 29:54.490
and cannot wait any longer.

29:55.750 --> 29:57.480
I only wish to witness Great Xia

29:58.110 --> 29:59.840
return from darkness to light.

30:00.070 --> 30:03.880
We pledge to serve
with all our might until our last breath.

30:10.200 --> 30:10.640
Du.

30:11.770 --> 30:13.230
The six of us once promised

30:13.510 --> 30:14.910
to be loyal to our country

30:14.960 --> 30:16.760
and serve in the court together.

30:16.790 --> 30:17.310
Now,

30:18.790 --> 30:19.790
you have departed

30:20.790 --> 30:21.720
while we stayed.

30:22.640 --> 30:24.000
We will do our utmost

30:24.590 --> 30:25.990
to support our wise ruler

30:26.110 --> 30:28.170
in hopes of bringing peace to the land

30:28.550 --> 30:30.480
and comfort your spirit in heaven.

30:30.830 --> 30:31.630
Rest assured,

30:32.160 --> 30:33.490
this day will come soon.

30:34.650 --> 30:36.980
The corrupt officials will pay the price.

30:37.350 --> 30:38.010
We will soon

30:39.290 --> 30:40.750
restore your reputation.

30:49.050 --> 30:59.230
[Tomb of Nameless]

31:03.310 --> 31:04.720
The weather is lovely today.

31:04.720 --> 31:06.070
Having you accompany me

31:06.200 --> 31:07.680
brings me great joy.

31:08.400 --> 31:09.720
Your Majesty, look.

31:10.000 --> 31:12.920
I designed these flower arrangements
for the Flower Festival Banquet.

31:12.920 --> 31:14.830
They're all the most precious varieties

31:14.830 --> 31:16.890
symbolizing prosperity and wealth.

31:17.510 --> 31:20.440
These flowers are indeed precious.

31:21.350 --> 31:23.870
But when arranged together,

31:24.310 --> 31:26.510
they look somewhat disorganized.

31:27.270 --> 31:29.350
Then Your Highness, please look at mine.

31:29.350 --> 31:30.960
These are all jasmine flowers

31:30.960 --> 31:32.680
with an enchanting fragrance.

31:32.680 --> 31:33.740
Please smell them.

31:36.510 --> 31:38.570
Jasmine indeed has a pure fragrance.

31:39.550 --> 31:42.790
But they look somewhat plain

31:43.200 --> 31:44.640
and rather shabby.

31:45.960 --> 31:47.160
Then, Your Highness,

31:47.550 --> 31:48.750
please look at these.

31:48.750 --> 31:50.110
Do you like orchids?

31:50.550 --> 31:54.010
Orchids from secluded valleys
have extraordinary elegance.

31:55.030 --> 31:57.240
Orchids are indeed refined.

31:58.200 --> 32:00.750
But we must consider the symbolism.

32:01.200 --> 32:03.400
After all,
they will be displayed in the palace.

32:03.400 --> 32:06.060
They should convey
grandeur and magnificence.

32:06.550 --> 32:07.440
Yes.

32:08.720 --> 32:10.240
A talented scholar's life

32:10.510 --> 32:12.510
is worth no more
than a handful of wildflowers.

32:12.510 --> 32:14.040
Yet to please the powerful,

32:14.310 --> 32:16.110
we exhaust ourselves thinking,

32:16.110 --> 32:17.270
wasting resources
and burdening the people.

32:17.270 --> 32:18.000
Consort Xie,

32:18.550 --> 32:19.880
what have you prepared?

32:22.550 --> 32:23.400
Your Majesty,

32:25.160 --> 32:26.290
I prepared peonies.

32:30.270 --> 32:31.030
Peonies?

32:32.510 --> 32:34.310
Isn't that too common?

32:35.030 --> 32:35.510
Right?

32:36.030 --> 32:37.000
You are right.

32:37.830 --> 32:39.490
Though this flower is common,

32:39.790 --> 32:41.390
the Flower Festival Banquet

32:41.790 --> 32:43.190
happens only once a year.

32:44.310 --> 32:46.570
This is about
Her Majesty's reputation.

32:48.350 --> 32:49.640
Her Majesty said

32:50.160 --> 32:52.110
we must not only consider
whether it is precious or not,

32:52.110 --> 32:53.970
but also their symbolic meaning.

32:54.350 --> 32:56.480
They cannot appear too shabby either.

33:01.960 --> 33:03.000
Beautiful peony,

33:04.030 --> 33:05.790
amidst a cluster of a hundred flowers

33:05.790 --> 33:07.920
your stunning radiance blooms alone.

33:12.070 --> 33:12.750
Peony,

33:14.160 --> 33:15.550
with the essence of all fragrances combined,

33:15.550 --> 33:18.110
fully displaying the grandeur of a prosperous age.

33:18.110 --> 33:20.440
Though they speak of your delicacy, laden with dew,

33:20.440 --> 33:21.400
your gentleness

33:22.640 --> 33:25.040
is like the spring breeze bringing warmth.

33:25.550 --> 33:28.110
Though they praise your nobility and overflowing scent—

33:28.110 --> 33:29.030
do they know?

33:30.000 --> 33:32.930
You have also endured the deepest cold and hardship.

33:32.960 --> 33:35.110
When the freezing snow sealed the earth,

33:35.110 --> 33:37.640
you were quietly nurturing a thousand hopes.

33:38.350 --> 33:40.550
And when the East Wind brushes the face,

33:41.920 --> 33:43.320
you take your prosperity

33:45.750 --> 33:47.550
and scatter it across the world.

33:51.750 --> 33:54.410
She recited
that long paragraph just like that?

33:54.960 --> 33:57.110
This flattery is way too obvious.

34:00.920 --> 34:01.850
Beautiful poem!

34:03.720 --> 34:04.880
Using flowers to symbolize people,

34:04.880 --> 34:06.080
subtle yet profound.

34:06.110 --> 34:06.840
Consort Xie,

34:07.160 --> 34:11.920
you truly embody scholarly elegance.

34:13.510 --> 34:15.960
No wonder the Emperor favors you so much.

34:18.590 --> 34:20.850
Thank you for your praise, Your Majesty.

34:21.880 --> 34:23.150
Unlike some people

34:24.440 --> 34:26.110
who lack proper manners.

34:27.920 --> 34:30.000
Why must everything involve me?

34:33.510 --> 34:35.239
What Flower Festival Banquet?

34:35.800 --> 34:38.280
I think they're just bored
and want to waste money.

34:38.280 --> 34:40.480
Common people can barely afford to eat,

34:41.110 --> 34:43.710
yet they still have time
for such frivolities.

34:47.280 --> 34:48.800
This isn't the way back to the palace.

34:48.800 --> 34:51.110
I didn't dare call out to you
since you were walking this way

34:51.110 --> 34:52.239
with your head down.

34:52.280 --> 34:52.920
No wonder.

34:53.070 --> 34:54.270
-Let's—
-Consort Yu.

34:57.710 --> 34:58.970
The palace is so large,

34:59.710 --> 35:01.590
yet somehow I run into him everywhere.

35:01.590 --> 35:02.440
Such bad luck.

35:02.960 --> 35:03.820
Your Highness.

35:07.920 --> 35:08.580
Consort Yu.

35:11.320 --> 35:12.550
May I have a word with you?
